Package polyglot.filemanager

Class ExtFileManager

java.lang.Object
javax.tools.ForwardingJavaFileManager<javax.tools.StandardJavaFileManager>
polyglot.filemanager.ExtFileManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Closeable, java.io.Flushable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, javax.tools.JavaFileManager, javax.tools.OptionChecker, javax.tools.StandardJavaFileManager, FileManager, SourceLoader, ClassFileLoader
public class ExtFileManager
extends javax.tools.ForwardingJavaFileManager<javax.tools.StandardJavaFileManager>
implements FileManager
FileManager implementation - A class that provides input and output access to the local file system. (NOTE: Extensions may extend this implementation and are not forced to use local file system for i/o.)
